<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>gẖnwạ ldm yswʿ ạlgẖạly</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (gẖnwạ ldm yswʿ ạlgẖạly .. ạlly ṣnʿ mnạ ạ̉bṭạl
 ạlly fdạnạ bslṭạn ʿạly .. bạlnʿmẗ lạ bạlạ̉ʿmạl)2
 (ạlḍʿyf ạ̹mtlạ kạsh .. ạlksyr byh rạfʿ rạsh)2
 (mạ fy sẖyʾ mʿạh mḥạl)2
 1- (ạldm mʿnạh ṣlyb .. wtmn dfʿh ḥml ạllh
 wmḥbẗ wḥb ʿjyb .. byh ạ̹mtznạ wạ̹ḥnạ kẖṭạẗ)2
 (lmạ qblth bạlạ̹ymạn .. ạ̉ʿṭạny byh ạlslṭạn)2
 ṣrt bdmh ạbn ạllh
 2- (lldm gẖlbẗ wslṭạn .. nsḥq byhạ kl qywd
 ạ̉y kẖṭyẗ mhmạ ạ̹n kạn .. ạ̉bdaⁿạ bạldm mạ tswd)2
 (lyh bnrfʿ ạ̉gẖnyạt .. wnʿly lyh ạlhtạfạt)2
 wnʿry ạlkdb ạlmwjwd
 3- (nʿln dmk ʿly̱ ạ̉ʿtạb .. kl bywtnạ wmạ lynạ
 ʿly̱ ḍmạyrnạ wkl ṣʿạb .. nṣbhạ ạlʿdw lynạ)2
 (wạtẖqyn fy dmk wfyk .. wfy slṭạn ạsmk wlyk)2
 bngẖny lk ạ̉gẖạnynạ</lyrics>
